# Copy to worker/.dev.vars and replace DEMO_KEY with your real key.
# DEMO_KEY is rate-limited to 30 requests/hour per IP — fine for a
# first-poke smoke test, useless for real development. Register at
# https://api.data.gov/signup/ — takes 30 seconds, gets you 1,000/hr.
# .dev.vars is gitignored. For production, use:
#   cd worker && npx wrangler secret put API_DATA_GOV_KEY
API_DATA_GOV_KEY=DEMO_KEY
